  </a>
</nav>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Retrospective · Jays Matchup Intel</div>
    <div class="header-title">RETRO <span>3-30-26</span></div>
    <div class="header-sub">TOR vs COL · Tomoyuki Sugano RHP · 73 pitches tracked</div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="score-box">
      <div class="score-label">Final Score</div>
      <div class="score-val">COL 14, TOR 5</div>
      <div class="score-note">Sugano only, Bayesian model scope</div>
    </div>
    <div class="aca-tag" style="margin-top:8px;">
      <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 300 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M178.57 127.15 290.27 0h-26.46l-97.03 110.38L89.34 0H0l117.13 166.93L0 300.25h26.46l102.41-116.59 81.8 116.59H300L178.57 127.15zm-36.18 41.19-11.87-16.64L36.16 19.54H76.8l76.26 106.89 11.87 16.64 99.06 138.89h-40.64l-80.96-113.62z" fill="white"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="aca-text">
        <div class="aca-name">Arm Chair Analyst</div>
        <div class="aca-handle">@scherrology</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tab-bar">
  <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab(0)">01 Arsenal Report Card</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(1)">02 Model Scorecard</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(2)">03 Deep Dive</div>
</div>

<div class="panel-wrap">

  <!-- TAB 1: ARSENAL REPORT CARD -->
  <div class="panel active" id="tab0">
    <div class="section-label">Predicted vs Actual · Pitch Mix and Velocity</div>
    <div class="section-title">Sugano went <em>off-script.</em></div>

    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Pitch Mix, Predicted vs Actual</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--text-dim);">
            <div style="width:24px;height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:1px;"></div> 2025 Projected
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--text-dim);">
            <div style="width:24px;height:6px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:1px;"></div> Tonight Actual
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="arsenalRows"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Key Deviations</div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
          <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(232,0,45,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(232,0,45,0.2);border-radius:3px;">
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--danger);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;">Significantly Reduced</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);">Sweeper, 8.3% tonight</div>
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:3px;">Projected 19.8%, down 11.5 points. His primary RHH weapon, shelved.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(45,212,160,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(45,212,160,0.2);border-radius:3px;">
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--success);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;">Significantly Increased</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);">4-Seam Fastball, 30.6% tonight</div>
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:3px;">Projected 18.9%, up 11.7 points. Came out fastball-heavy from the start.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(196,162,75,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(196,162,75,0.2);border-radius:3px;">
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;">Elevated</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);">Cutter, 20.8% tonight</div>
            <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:3px;">Projected 12.0%, up 8.8 points. Used it to generate weak contact and the Springer HR.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Velocity, On Target</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--success);">+0.4 to +1.6</div>
        <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:4px;">mph above 2025 avg across all pitches</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.5;">Velo was not the story tonight. All pitches were at or slightly above 2025 season averages. The deviation was pitch selection, not stuff.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Zone Tendency</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--warning);">Zone 14</div>
        <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:4px;">12 of 40 RHH pitches, low away ball</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.5;">Consistent with 2025 tendencies. He worked low and away to RHH all night, setting up the fastball up in the zone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Scouting Grade</div>
