      <strong style="color:var(--white);">Context:</strong> With 2 PA per hitter, variance is expected and the model does not claim to predict individual game outcomes with precision. At this sample size, the model's job is to identify who is best positioned over a series of opportunities. Springer delivered. Sánchez showed the LHH angle we flagged. The miss pattern (5 of 8 hitters at .000) reflects Sugano's off-script pitch mix as much as model error.
